jo kuJ (Akwl purK ny auhnW BMfwirAW ivc) pwieAw hY ieko vwrI pw id`qw hY, (Bwv, aus dy BMfwry sdw AKu`t hn)[
isRStI nUM pYdw krn vwlw Akwl purK (jIvW nUM) pYdw kr ky (auhnW dI) sMBwl kr irhw hY[
hy nwnk! sdw-iQr rihx vwly (Akwl purK) dI (isRStI dI sMBWl vwlI) ieh kwr sdw At`l hY (aukweI qoN ^wlI hY)[
